<li><a href="http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=7238828" class="external text" title="http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=7238828" rel="nofollow">NPR interview</a></li>
<li><a href="http://theeveningclass.blogspot.com/2007/01/das-leben-der-anderen-lives-of.html" class="external text" title="http://theeveningclass.blogspot.com/2007/01/das-leben-der-anderen-lives-of.html" rel="nofollow">The Evening Class interview</a></li>
<li><a href="http://film.virtual-history.com/film.php?filmid=23236" class="external text" title="http://film.virtual-history.com/film.php?filmid=23236" rel="nofollow">Movie stills</a></li>
