<li><a href="http://www.newyorker.com/arts/critics/cinema/2007/02/12/070212crci_cinema_lane" class="external text" title="http://www.newyorker.com/arts/critics/cinema/2007/02/12/070212crci_cinema_lane" rel="nofollow"><i>The New Yorker</i> magazine review</a></li>
